Package users

Class User

java.lang.Object
users.User
All Implemented Interfaces:
IUser
Direct Known Subclasses:
Staff, Student
public abstract class User
extends java.lang.Object
implements IUser
Abstract base class representing a user in the system. Contains common attributes and functionality shared by all user types. This class implements the IUser interface and provides the core implementation for user management in the system.
See Also:
IUser
